      "event_id": "mh_whisper",
      "title": "The Whisper Vote",
      "description": "It starts as grumbling in the mess and hardens into a proposal: the AI has cost them too much, and the ship would be safer flying itself. The AI hears every word and can answer none of them without seeming to plead.",
